phrases: Man, we have exams coming up,
and these girls could not care less about studying.
Have you still not gotten in contact with Miku?
I think her phone's turned off.
She told me where she went.
If Yotsuba cannot say no, you can say no for her.
You are good at impersonating each other, are you not?
I am not that good at it.
Remember what happened when I tried to impersonate Ichika?
As soon as Miku arrives, we will have her wear your track suit, and..
We need to act before they get to the station!
I am not going home, no matter what.
You are going to make yourself sick with all that sugar.
You are such a child, not appreciating this refined taste.
Leave once you are done drinking that.
How did you even find out where my new hotel was?
I went to your last hotel the day before.
What were you doing with Futaro?
If I had to describe what happened the day before yesterday in one word...
I am never going to forgive that bastard.
Wh-What did he do to you?
Why are not you making more of a reaction?!
I mean, that is something we do all the time.
He also said he wanted the five of us to stick together.
He said that after I told him my situation.
Do not you want to come home, Nino?
What is the point of sticking together when we are all so far apart?
I guess you think we have all changed,
but from my perspective, you have changed a lot, too.
You never used to drink black tea before.
We are all still one-fifth of a person, scoring a twenty each.
Hey, I never said you could look!
The answer is Battle of Nagashino.
What, are you trying to show off because you studied?
I have always liked Sengoku warlords.
But I would never have known what this tastes like if you were not around.
It is true that the five of us used to be identical,
and we never got into arguments or trouble.
But we would have always stayed at a twenty that way.
We should laugh, get angry, feel sad,
complementing each other where we fall short
and grow into the people we are meant to be.
So it is all right that we are different.
By the way, with you gone,
the food at home is a disaster.
We do not have a balanced diet.
That is for you to figure out yourselves!
I never would have thought to drink something like this.
Black tea starts off bitter, too.
It is a classy kind of bitter.
It definitely comes from high-quality tea leaves.
The bitterness of green tea has depth.
I am sure it uses better leaves.
Fine, I will look it up.
Do not go crying if it turns out that they use weeds for green tea.
Black tea and green tea use the same tea leaves.
The difference is the amount of fermentation?
I need to tell the rest of the gir...
I need to forget the past and accept the present.
Maybe it is time to brace myself.
You would best brace yourself, too, Miku.
I-I would like to leave the team.
I already want to quit this role!
Itsuki, you are Yotsuba right now.
You, at least, look perfectly like her.
Are you sure this is going to work?
I do not have a choice anymore.
I cannot go to training camp.
I would like to leave the team.
Exams are coming up next week.
Why is someone pretending to be Nakano-san?
Why did you stoop to groping?
I lied to lure you away!
Itsuki is requesting your resignation in your place.
Yeah, you look alike, but you are not her.
Your hair's not the right length.
You need to show more interest in other people!
Thank you for worrying for me.
But I am sorry, I am going.
Oh, I see, it was a joke.
Though, it is true that I want to quit.
I mean, you have to be out of your mind to start a training camp right before exams.
If you had not brought Miku...
When I arrived at the hotel, I saw Miku standing there with a pair of scissors.
I do not know what exactly happened,
but she must have had a change of heart.
I cannot believe you cut it so short.
Did you have you heart broken or something?
Just so you know, it was not you.
I just did as I was asked.
We did not have to do this.
I am sure she would have understood if you would talked to her honestly.
It sucks, but it cannot be all bad.
Want me to come with you?
Thanks, but I will be all right by myself.
I was the one who was wrong.
If you were wrong about anything,
it was how hard you hit me.
I was going to give this to you as a token of my apology.
Presale tickets for the movie you said you wanted to see the other day.
Let us go watch it together.
Why does nothing ever work out the way you want it to?
I am deeply sorry for the trouble I have caused.
I have spoken with the track team.
I will help them with the meet, and then part ways with them.
You are still hung up on that?
It looks like we have all finished our problem sets.
I do not know if we have leveled up at all.
I-I did not think you would be the kind of person.
What is the point of getting good grades if we have to cheat?!
I am whipping you into shape in the last two days so you do not have to resort to this!
May I move forward with this plan?
Why would you even ask after how much you have done already?
I got all of the questions wrong.
You said you were smart, but you are all talk, huh?
Why are you going out of your way for us?
I am never having you teach me!
You should never have come into our lives!
He said he is calling Raiha-chan.
because his phone's out of battery.
The five of you together are unstoppable.
This is the best we could do after how much we studied?

I guess we really are stupid.
You need to worry about yourself.
Today happens to be tutoring day, too.
I guess we are going to spend today reviewing the finals.
Futaro's going to give us an earful.
Why do you sound so happy about it?
It is too bad we did not do better,
but I cannot wait to work with you guys again.
Are you not driving for Dad today?
I am here today as your temporary tutor.
Ebata-san used to be a teacher, after all.
I wonder if he is sick or something.
I received word from your father the other day
that Uesugi-sama terminating his contract as of the exam the other day.
It is because of how we did on the exam.
I do not believe that is the case.
I am told that Uesugi-sama resigned of his own accord.
I will call him over and talk to him myself.
I am afraid that will not be possible.
Uesugi-sama is forbidden from ever setting foot into this home.
Though temporarily, I am tasked with tutoring you.
I cannot let you go until I teach you a certain amount.
We can go once we are done with this, right?
Ebata-san must be going easy on us.
I do not know if we could have solved these in the past, though.
It is almost weird how easy the problems are.
I hate to admit it, but it is all thanks to him.
It is just one more problem.
I am down to the last one, too.
I shall have to start a special lesson
if you are not able to make it through those problems.
Want to look at the crib sheet?
You mean the one from the final?
We should all have it in our pencil cases.
The ends will justify the means.
I guess I will, too, then.
Do not try to take shortcuts to the answer, fools.
Do not try to take shortcuts to the answer, fools.
He never intended to let us cheat from the beginning.
What do we do now, though?
I am not going to teach cheaters.
I am not going to teach cheaters.
You have to get there yourselves from now on.
You have to get there yourselves from now on.
I am glad I am finally done with this hell job.
I am glad I am finally done with this hell job.
But it was a pretty fun hell.
But it was a pretty fun hell.
I still want Uesugi-san to teach me.
But he cannot come here anymore.
There is nothing we can do.
Please, Ebata-san, give us a hand.
You have grown up so much.
Would you like to buy some cake?
We would like one delivered to our home.
I will handle it from here.
This is not the way to your place.
Hey, I am sorry I did not tell you I was quitting.
But I cannot go back to tutoring anymore.
We wanted you to see this.
I am glad it did not take too long to find a new one.
A graduate from a university in Tokyo and a former teacher.
He seems like he is up to the task.
Are you really just going to leave us with the next person and abandon us?
and I failed to produce results.
There is no guarantee I will do better on the next exam.
I had to give the job to a professional.
It is the right thing to do.
I cannot let you suffer for my selfish ends any more.
Thanks to that, we had to study against our will.
We had to memorize and learn formulas like crazy.
But we ended up happy when we could solve problems.
It is all your fault that we made it this far!
You cannot stop being selfish now!
I am not even allowed to go back into your home.
I am making a decent amount of money, after all.
We are going to be living here from now on.
Now there is nothing in our way.
You let go of your place just for that?
Like we talked about before, it is not where we are that matters.
It is that the five of us are together!
I think you are someone who is needed now.
My life's flashing before my eyes.
Is not this all a little too recent, though?
What good is it if we all jump in?!
Please do not give up after just two tries.
We can do it this time.
Open that once you learn to accept yourself.
You need to think before you act.
And I am getting sick of trying to be considerate.
I am going to do as I please, too.
You would better put up with my selfishness,
all the way to the end.
This is not what I think it is.
Since that is settled, let us go inside.
We are going to eat the cake without you.
How are you going to split it into five if I join?
